class="post" id="post-42254"><h2>PC Vs. Mac</h2><div
class="entry"><div
style="height:33px;" class="really_simple_share robots-nocontent snap_nopreview"><div
class="really_simple_share_facebook_like" style="width:100px;"> <iframe
src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Ftech-seeker.com%2Fblog%2Fpc-vs-mac%2F&amp;layout=button_count&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=100&amp;action=like&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;send=false&amp;height=27"
