class="comment"> <img
alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/43fcd0ddb816877d58a99a0e740eb147?s=32&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' /><cite>Ethan</cite> Says: <br
